abstract: The Times's Connor Ennis looks at which candidates are about to face a gauntlet of tough conference tests, and which ones can remain on cruise control.
snippet: The Times's Connor Ennis looks at which candidates are about to face a gauntlet of tough conference tests, and which ones can remain on cruise control.
lead_paragraph: Russel Wilson vaulted himself into the front-runner conversation, while other Heisman candidates continue to stay the course. The Times's Connor Ennis looks at which candidates are about to face a gauntlet of tough conference tests, and which ones can remain on cruise control.
